data.description: Celebrate holidays in this beautiful 4bed/4bath home that's meticulously maintained & move in ready. This floor plan will wow you &  perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing w/family. Enter living room w/flood of natural light and hardwood floors that are throughout main level. Float into dining area which seats 4-12 & set your gaze on updated eat-in kitchen of 42"custom cabs, ctr island where microwave reside, SS appliances, granite, tile backsplash & ample counter space. Great room boasts builtins, bay windows, & WB FPL. 2 car oversized garage doubles as an ideal mancave w/heater, ceiling fan, cables to hook up & watch those games as you work on the workbench. Primary features ensuite w/ walkin closet & updated bathroom w/ soaker & sep shower & dbl sinks. LL boasts rec room w/gas FPL, FULL kitchen w/SS appliances, 36" cabs & counters. &  full bath. Beautiful landscaping & level backyard w/patio & special big toys for tots. Don't forget the club pool and stocked pond.
